sections.heading: of podiatry; approval; requirements
sections.text: No school of podiatry shall be approved by the board unless the school is accredited by the Council on Podiatric Medical Education of the American Podiatric Medical Association.SourceLaws 1927, c. 167, ยง 75, p. 474;C.S.1929, ยง 71-1004;R.S.1943, ยง 71-176;Laws 1947,
